________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
  	USBtoUART converter		|		EasyVR shield		|		Color
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
		RXD			|		12 (RX)			|		Azul
		TXD			|		13 (TX)			|		Verde


________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
	USBtoUART converter		|		Raspberry Pi		|		Color
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
		RXD			|	UART_TXD (GPIO 14)		|		Azul
		TXD			|	UART_RXD (GPIO 15)		|		Verde


